==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Free-living
<hw>Free"-liv`ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Unrestrained indulgence of
the appetites as a way of life.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>free-living</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: free-living
<hw>free-living</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <fld>(Biology)</fld> <def>Living
independently of other organisms; not parasitic or commensal.</def>
<note>eating other organisms is not considered "dependence" in this
sense.</note>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> nonparasitic, nonsymbiotic.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Free-love</ent>⟦br⟧
